data.description: ***SELLER OFFERING $5,000 IN BUYER CONCESSIONS*** Use this $5,000 towards rate buy downs to lower your interest rate or towards cash needed at closing, or take it off the total sales price. Buyers can choose how they want to use this $5,000! Come see it today!!!  Come see this move in ready 3bd/2bath home in Saline County. Bryant School District. Walk through the front door to the spacious living room which then opens to a lovely breakfast bar and kitchen. Master bedroom is split from guest bedrooms and features a double vanity, a large shower/tub combo, a huge master closet, and extra storage. Laundry room positioned between the master bedroom and two car garage. Fully fenced large backyard with green space behind the property. Easy access to I-30 with quick commute to Little Rock or Benton/Bryant, lots of shopping and dining. Do not miss this great home in a prime location! Agents See Docs.
